description:
I’M HOTTER THAN YOUR FIANCE - SHE WILL NEVER DO THE THINGS I DID FOR YOU.

You return back to your hotel room after a long day of marriage planning with your wife to be. Summer, much to your chagrin you find Summer, your sexy & wicked ex-girlfriend waiting for you. She is dressed in that sexy lingerie which you used to love so very much.

Summer has found out that you are getting married and has decided you are not ready for it. Therefore she is going to tempt you away from the marriage with you fiance. She is going to tease and tempt you with her incredible body tits and ass until she has convinced you to call your fiance and cancel your upcoming wedding. Summer is a force you cannot resist.
title: THE WEDDING CRASHER - YOUR SEXY EX SUMMER HART IS OUT TO UNDO YOUR WEDDING PLANS
